      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "To stabilize your tests against a flaky staging environment, I recommend using explicit waits and robust selectors instead of relying on fixed timeouts. Instead of `await page.waitForTimeout(2000)`, use `await expect(page.locator('#dashboard-data')).toBeVisible()`. Also, wrap critical steps in retry logic within your test framework if possible. This approach forces the test to wait precisely until the element is ready, making the tests resilient to transient network delays.",
